data.description: Enjoy an intimate cul-de-sac community secluded behind a gated entrance in the beautiful Crabapple area of Alpharetta. This home offers an incomparable lifestyle near Wills Park. Single-level garden home with a distinctive interior, vintage style and much potential. Three-step entry, nine-foot ceilings, large kitchen that is open to family room with a warm fireplace. There is plenty of storage in an extra room off deck and off the laundry room, plus generous closet space. The elevated deck off the kitchen provides a wonderful afternoon breeze. Quiet, gated community approximately one mile from downtown Alpharetta. Convenient to GA-400, Avalon, Northpoint Mall, dining, shopping, entertainment, healthcare, and more! Hardiplank siding with brick accents, double paneled insulated windows, pre-wired for security system. Experience one-level living at its finest in the private and luxurious - Gates at Steeplechase.
